      "rationale": "Richardson extrapolation across three mesh refinements yields GCI of 2.1% for the normalised hemolysis index at the adult nominal point. Discretisation error is within the required threshold. Study was performed exclusively at adult flow conditions (4.5 L/min); no equivalent mesh study exists for the paediatric flow regime added in Q1 2025."
