      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 2,
      "achievedLevel": 2,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Predicted NIH within ±20% of measured NIH at all validation points; relative hemolysis index RH < 1.",
      "rationale": "CFD-predicted NIH values agree with measured values within ±15% across all five adult operating points. RH < 1 satisfied for all predicate comparisons within the validated adult envelope. Comparison metrics are not available for the paediatric flow range (0.8–1.5 L/min) as no corresponding experimental data were collected."
    },
    {
