      "rationale": "MRL 2 does not require formal numerical solver error quantification beyond residual monitoring. Residuals converge to 10^-5 for all continuity, momentum, and turbulence equations. Factor scoped to not-assessed in accordance with MRL 2 requirements table."
    },
