      "acceptanceCriteria": "Not assessed at MRL 2; analyst training records reviewed.",
      "rationale": "Analyst holds CFD certification and completed internal training on hemolysis modelling workflows. Formal use-error assessment not required at MRL 2. Factor noted as not-assessed per credibility matrix."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Model form",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 2,
      "achievedLevel": 2,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Turbulence model and hemolysis power-law exponents selected based on literature evidence for blood pump applications.",
      "rationale": "SST k-omega turbulence model selected based on published benchmark studies for rotating blood-contacting devices. Giersiepen-Wurzinger power-law hemolysis model with Bludszuweit correction applied. Model form uncertainty acknowledged as a primary contributor to NIH prediction error; within acceptable bounds for MRL 2."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Model inputs",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 2,
