      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Fluid properties, boundary conditions, and geometric parameters traceable to measurements or published standards.",
      "rationale": "Blood viscosity and density specified per ASTM F1841 analogue fluid properties. Pump geometry from manufacturer-supplied CAD with dimensional inspection report. Inlet velocity profiles derived from Doppler ultrasound measurements. All inputs documented in simulation input specification log. Input ranges cover adult operating conditions; paediatric-specific input characterisation (e.g., reduced blood viscosity in neonates) has not been separately assessed."
